"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"「黎明星」真係失蹤????? 有 D 心寒 post......<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahAkLfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahAkLfU</a>"},{"pid":"21c9483da8841d5f98026d251ce32f348e875d9b","tid":1576644,"uid":52897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"都似係咁"},{"pid":"8534e565a09ed3b541c1f12bbf4c01883e1737f4","tid":1576644,"uid":210009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f137d3bab2248dd3280837a6e1ab5bb33a5b242","tid":1576644,"uid":192824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"「黎明星」真係失蹤????? 有 D 心寒 post......<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahAkLfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahAkLfU</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個都有機會"},{"pid":"2dfa18f3e206fcae5a692d772826af91dfe9fe9c","tid":1576644,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4cb708fc30bbeddf7ed5962748566510e26ac5","tid":1576644,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4fe19ad08d41d00feaae67fe0b9bcaf4c3596ef","tid":1576644,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5787b76d3643185954f83508e81e97e5f4eae091","tid":1576644,"uid":66578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e13b89020fdaf674f848a447fd4390ab7f3ad","tid":1576644,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"拆穿都冇用<br />\n班藍屍根本就覺得驚賊殺人都冇所謂"},{"pid":"0384abf95d5b77db4e1af12a9f686ea47faed7d7","tid":1576644,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"363e13b89020fdaf674f848a447fd4390ab7f3ad","tid":1576644,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"拆穿都冇用<br />\n班藍屍根本就覺得驚賊殺人都冇所謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"唔理班藍絲點睇，我淨係想知真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}